Hi Cal,
Actually the 1963 VW Transporter Workshop Manual list the 1955-63 axle nuts 
to 215 ft. lbs., the 1964-67 as 215-250 ft. lbs., so knock off the slight 
bouncing. :-)  As for the FW to crank gland bolt only uses 217 ft. lbs.!   
